          <p>We came up with this idea of Team Share, where a subscriber could share entire articles or snippets of content with members of their team, whether or not they are subscribers themselves. They could highlight sections and add their own comments to the article, to kick off a discussion with their team that would take place in this Team Share experience. We introduced the concept of limiting the amount of time the content would be available, to incentivize members to interact with and comment on the content.</p>

