        <h3 class="article__heading">Outcome</h3>
        <p>In order to give the HBR team as much confidence on a path forward as we could, we did two additional weeks of user testing and iteration with our Sprint prototype. We facilitated seven interviews where we asked background questions and received feedback on our prototype. After the first four interviews, we iterated on our prototype to address any common questions or pitfalls that caused any hiccups or confusions. After we completed the final round of interviews, we synthesized our feedback and presented our findings and recommendations to the HBR team at large.</p>

